{
  "uuid": "e21f00514e79aa1fdae9c9aa5eab78b1",
  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Waiter/Waitress",
  "description": "<p>Singaporean / Singapore PR / LTVP holders only.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Overview:</strong></p><p>We are seeking a friendly, professional, and attentive Waiter/Waitress to join our front-of-house team. As a key part of the guest experience, you will be responsible for providing exceptional service, ensuring guest satisfaction, and helping to create a welcoming and enjoyable dining atmosphere.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Greet guests warmly and guide them to their tables.</li><li>Present menus, answer questions about dishes and dietary options, and make recommendations when requested.</li><li>Take accurate food and beverage orders and input them into the POS system.</li><li>Serve food and beverages in a timely and courteous manner.</li><li>Ensure guest satisfaction throughout the meal and address any concerns promptly.</li><li>Clear and reset tables between courses and after each guest.</li><li>Communicate effectively with kitchen and bar staff to ensure smooth service flow.</li><li>Handle payments and provide accurate change or process card transactions.</li><li>Maintain cleanliness and organization of the dining area and workstations.</li><li>Follow health, safety, and hygiene standards at all times.</li><li>Requirements:</li><li>Previous experience in a front-of-house or customer service role is preferred.</li><li>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills.</li><li>A positive attitude and ability to work well in a team.</li><li>Strong attention to detail and multitasking abilities.</li><li>Flexibility to work evenings, weekends, and holidays.</li><li>Ability to remain calm and composed under pressure.</li><li>Professional appearance and demeanor.</li></ul><p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p><p>* 5 working days</p><p>* Staff meals provided</p><p>* Staff discount at Pera</p><p>* Opportunities for training and development</p><p>* A chance to be part of an exciting new restaurant</p>",
